# Project Overview and Architecture

## Core Architecture

This is a mobile-first Progressive Web App (PWA) built with Next.js App Router for collecting train stations. The main entry points are:

- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main landing page
- [app/collection/page.tsx](mdc:app/collection/page.tsx) - Collection overview
- [app/search/page.tsx](mdc:app/search/page.tsx) - Station search interface